[Scene01]

The time had finally come, and led by Bob, the Blobs amassed around the
Biomech Tower. From there they would descend into the courtyard and
fight one of the biggest battles in the Blob's history. But there
were still a few obstacles to overcome.

[Scene02]

The main doors of the Tower would be sealed tight and so another way
to penetrate the tower's high walls would be needed. Together Bob
and Teeka would make their way around the Tower's perimeter and
enter via a service tunnel. Once there they would lower the Tower's
counter teleport systems and the final battle would commence...

[END]
